  "instructions": [
    "Heat the rendered lamb fat in a large cazuela over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the shredded cabbage, salt, black pepper, cumin, and coriander, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Uncover and cook for an additional 10 minutes, stirring frequently, until the cabbage is tender and slightly caramelized.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley or cilantro, if desired."
